). Arrange dumplings in Varoma dish and on Varoma tray and set aside."},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Beetroot soup"},{"content":"Place beetroot in mixing bowl and chop <b>3 sec\/speed 4.5<b>."},{"content":"Add water, white wine, vegetable stock paste, flour, salt, nutmeg and black pepper and mix <b>5 sec\/speed 3<b>."},{"content":"Set Varoma dish and tray in position and cook <b>25 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>."},{"content":"Set Varoma aside, add cream and white wine vinegar to mixing bowl, insert measuring cup and blend <b>1 min 30 sec\/speed 5<b>-<strong>10, increasing speed gradually.<\/strong> Season to taste. Transfer soup to bowls, add dumplings and serve hot."}],"basicInfo":["medium","35m","1h 10m","6 portions"]}